        <mxCell id="title" value="&lt;b&gt;BPMN AS-IS — Turno a Cobro&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Current manual process with Geovet + WhatsApp + external calendar duplication" style="text;html=1;align=left;fontSize=16" vertex="1" parent="1">
