        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="notes" value="&lt;b&gt;SCOPE — what to interview for&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;bull; Every step where info is copied between Geovet and external calendar&lt;br&gt;&amp;bull; Who confirms the turno (recepción? Paula? the vet?)&lt;br&gt;&amp;bull; When / how the cliente gets notified (manual WhatsApp? nothing?)&lt;br&gt;&amp;bull; Cancellation / no-show rules in practice vs on paper&lt;br&gt;&amp;bull; Payment moment — consulta end vs next visit vs never?&lt;br&gt;&amp;bull; Who enters the charge into Geovet?&lt;br&gt;&amp;bull; What goes wrong most often (the real pain points)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Interview targets: Paula + recepción (pendiente) + Valdemar + Fernanda." style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=11;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=6" vertex="1" parent="1">
